    {
      "kind": "guardrails",
      "reason": "CMM-FR-130..138 OPA policies (hipaa.rego, cms_code_mutual_exclusion, cms_time_thresholds, consent_required, rpm_16day_rule, tcm_window, apcm_tier_eligibility, rac_audit_trail, fqhc_rhc_g0511) require guardrail-service policy materialization, which Core does not expose as a pack surface yet. The behavioral guarantees are partially covered today by Core invariants (proposal-mode + four-eyes approval on every billing decision \u2014 BR-2) plus the same rules encoded as retrievable grounding memories and the case-triage agent's instructions."
    },
    {
      "kind": "eval_sets",
